---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Therapy" description="Individual therapy for anxiety, depression, relational issues, and life transitions. Learn about working with Katie d'Autremont, LCSW.">
  <section class="py-24 px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-6 text-center">One-on-One Therapy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal-light text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Deep, ongoing work for those ready to explore patterns, process emotions, and create lasting change.
      </p>

      <!-- Who It's For -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-6">Who This Is For</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light mb-6">
          I work with adults who are navigating:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-charcoal-light">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sage mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-charcoal">Anxiety</strong> — persistent worry, racing thoughts, difficulty being present</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sage mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-charcoal">Depression</strong> — low mood, lack of motivation, feeling stuck</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sage mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-charcoal">Relational issues</strong> — patterns in relationships, boundaries, communication</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sage mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-charcoal">Life transitions</strong> — career changes, moves, identity shifts, becoming a parent</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light mt-6">
          My ideal clients have some stability in their lives and are genuinely curious about themselves. You don't need to have it all figured out — but you're ready to look inward and do the work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What Sessions Are Like -->
      <div class="mb-12 bg-sage/5 p-8 rounded-xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-6">What Sessions Are Like</h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light mb-6">
          Sessions are 50 minutes, held weekly or biweekly depending on your needs. We meet via secure video.
        </p>
        <p class="text-charcoal-light">
          My approach is collaborative and insight-oriented. We'll explore patterns, process emotions, and work toward the changes you want to make. I draw from various evidence-based approaches, tailored to what works for you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Logistics -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl mb-6">Logistics</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-2">Session Format</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">50-minute sessions via secure telehealth</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-2">Frequency</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">Weekly or biweekly</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-2">Rates</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">Available upon request</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-cream-dark">
            <p class="font-medium text-charcoal mb-2">Insurance</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">Out-of-network; superbills provided</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-sage text-cream px-12 py-6 rounded-md hover:bg-sage-dark transition-colors font-medium">
          Request a Consultation
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-warm-gray mt-4">
          Free 15-minute call to see if we're a good fit
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Disclaimer -->
      <div class="bg-cream-dark/50 p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-sage">
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light mb-4">
          <strong class="text-charcoal">Licensing Note:</strong> I am licensed to provide therapy to clients located in [State(s)]. If you're outside these areas, I'd be happy to help you find a provider in your state.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-light">
          <strong class="text-charcoal">Crisis Resources:</strong> If you are in immediate danger or experiencing a mental health crisis, please call 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline), text HOME to 741741 (Crisis Text Line), or go to your nearest emergency room.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
